&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a self-motivated highly organised individual to join our secretarial team supporting the Division of Medicine Management Team in the day to day office functions, diary management, telephone handling, minute taking and typing correspondence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates with previous secretarial/personal assistant experience is essential. A thorough knowledge of Microsoft office applications is a key requisite along with excellent communication and organisational skills.&lt;/p&gt;
